ont-family:Arial Narrow;\">13.</span></td>\n									<td style=\"text-align: justify;\" valign=\"top\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial Narrow;\">Memberikan informasi lainnya mengenai HSSE yang berkaitan dengan kontrak ini.</span></td>\n								</tr>\n							</tbody>\n						</table>\n						</td>\n					</tr>\n				</tbody>\n			</table>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"text-align: justify;\" valign=\"top\">&nbsp;</td>\n			<td valign=\"top\">\n			<table align=\"left\" style=\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;\">\n				<tbody>\n					<tr>\n						<td style=\"width: 6.5%; text-align: justify;\" valign=\"top\">&nbsp;</td>\n						<td style=\"text-align: justify;\" valign=\"top\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial Narrow;\"><strong>KONTRAKTOR&nbsp;</strong>dapat mengembangkan HSSE Plan yang berisi informasi risiko HSSE lainnya dengan mengacu kepada draft HSSE plan di atas.</span></td>\n					</tr>\n				</tbody>\n			</table>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"text-align: justify;\" valign=\"top\">&nbsp;</td>\n			<td valign=\"top\">\n			<table align=\"left\" style=\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;\">\n				<tbody>\n					<tr>\n						<td style=\"width: 6.5%; text-align: justify;\" valign=\"top\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial Narrow;\">b.</span></td>\n						<td style=\"text-align: justify;\" valign=\"top\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial Narrow;\">Persyaratan APD</span></td>\n					</tr>\n				</tbody>\n			</table>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"text-align: justify;\" valign=\"top\">&nbsp;</td>\n			<td valign=\"top\">\n			<table align=\"left\" style=\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;\">\n				<tbody>\n					<tr>\n						<td style=\"width: 6.5%; text-align: justify;\" valign=\"top\">&nbsp;</td>\n						<td style=\"text-align: justify;\" valign=\"top\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial Narrow;\">Semua pekerja&nbsp;<strong>KONTRAKTOR&nbsp;</strong>yang bekerja di area&nbsp;<strong>PERUSAHAAN&nbsp;</strong>dan atau workshop&nbsp;<strong>KONTRAKTOR&nbsp;</strong>wajib mematuhi persyaratan minimum sebagai berikut :</span></td>\n					</tr>\n				</tbody>\n			</table>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"text-align: justify;\" valign=\"top\">&nbsp;</td>\n			<td valign=\"top\">\n			<table align=\"left\" style=\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;\">\n				<tbody>\n					<tr>\n						<td style=\"width: 6.5%; text-align: justify;\" valign=\"top\">&nbsp;</td>\n						<td valign=\"top\">\n						<table align=\"left\" style=\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;\">\n							<tbody>\n								<tr>\n									<td style=\"width: 6.5%; text-align: justify;\" valign=\"top\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial Narrow;\">1.</span></td>\n									<td style=\"text-align: justify;\" valign=\"top\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial Narrow;\"><em>Safety Vest</em>.</span></td>\n								</tr>\n							</tbody>\n						</table>\n						</td>\n					</tr>\n				</tbody>\n			</table>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"text-align: justify;\" valign=\"top\">&nbsp;</td>\n			<td valign=\"top\">\n			<table align=\"left\" style=\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;\">\n				<tbody>\n					<tr>\n						<td style=\"width: 6.5%; text-align: justify;\" valign=\"top\">&nbsp;</td>\n						<td valign=\"top\">\n						<table align=\"left\" style=\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;\">\n							<tbody>\n								<tr>\n									<td style=\"width: 6.5%; text-align: justify;\" valign=\"top\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial Narrow;\">2.</span></td>\n									<td style=\"text-align: justify;\" valign=\"top\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial Narrow;\">Sepatu keselamatan</span></td>\n								</tr>\n							</tbody>\n						</table>\n						</td>\n					</tr>\n				</tbody>\n			</table>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"text-align: justify;\" valign=\"top\">&nbsp;</td>\n			<td valign=\"top\">\n			<table align=\"left\" style=\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;\">\n				<tbody>\n					<tr>\n						<td style=\"width: 6.5%; text-align: justify;\" valign=\"top\">&nbsp;</td>\n						<td valign=\"top\">\n						<table align=\"left\" style=\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;\">\n							<tbody>\n								<tr>\n									<td style=\"width: 6.5%; text-align: justify;\" valign=\"top\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial Narrow;\">3.</span></td>\n									<td style=\"text-align: justify;\" valign=\"top\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial Narrow;\">Helm dengan tali dagu.</span></td>\n								</tr>\n							</tbody>\n						</table>\n						</td>\n					</tr>\n				</tbody>\n			</table>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"text-align: justify;\" valign=\"top\">&nbsp;</td>\n			<td valign=\"top\">\n			<table align=\"left\" style=\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;\">\n				<tbody>\n					<tr>\n						<td style=\"width: 6.5%; text-align: justify;\" valign=\"top\">&nbsp;</td>\n						<td valign=\"top\">\n						<table align=\"left\" style=\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;\">\n							<tbody>\n								<tr>\n									<td style=\"width: 6.5%; text-align: justify;\" valign=\"top\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial Narrow;\">4.</span></td>\n									<td style=\"text-align: justify;\" valign=\"top\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial Narrow;\"><em>Safety full body harness double lanyard</em>.</span></td>\n								</tr>\n							</tbody>\n						</table>\n						</td>\n					</tr>\n				</tbody>\n			</table>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"text-align: justify;\" valign=\"top\">&nbsp;</td>\n			<td valign=\"top\">\n			<table align=\"left\" style=\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;\">\n				<tbody>\n					<tr>\n						<td style=\"width: 6.5%; text-align: justify;\" valign=\"top\">&nbsp;</td>\n						<td valign=\"top\">\n						<table align=\"left\" style=\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;\">\n							<tbody>\n								<tr>\n									<td style=\"width: 6.5%; text-align: justify;\" valign=\"top\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial Narrow;\">5.</span></td>\n									<td style=\"text-align: justify;\" valign=\"top\"><span style=\"fon